<template>
  <vue-cal
  :time="false"
  hide-weekends 
  :disable-views="disable_views"
  
  />
</template>


<script>

import VueCal from 'vue-cal'
import 'vue-cal/dist/vuecal.css'

export default {
  name: 'YourComponent',
  components: {
    VueCal,
  },
  data() {
    return {
        disable_views : ['years', 'year', 'week']
      
    };
  },
};
</script>
